    "improvements_made": "1. Replaced separate ADDRESS and CONTACT entities with a unified CONTACT_INFO entity to streamline contact handling and support address as a contact type. 2. Added DONOR_ORGANIZATION junction table and changed the donor‑organization relationship to optional many‑to‑many, allowing donors to support multiple charities. 3. Introduced optional activity_id in MESSAGE to link communications to specific event activities. 4. Added donation_status attribute to DONATION for audit‑trail (pending, completed, refunded, etc.). 5. Standardized datetime attribute names across EVENT and EVENT_ACTIVITY (start_datetime, end_datetime). 6. Updated relationships and cardinalities to reflect the new structures while preserving existing strengths."
